	<article id="post-871" class="post-871 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-citizenship category-ethnicity category-latin-america category-the-sociology-of-citizenship">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.qeh.ox.ac.uk/?p=871" title="Permalink to Plurinational citizenship in the making" rel="bookmark">Plurinational citizenship in the making</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://blog.qeh.ox.ac.uk/?p=871" title="12:02 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-02-19T12:02:39+00:00" pubdate>February 19, 2015</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.qeh.ox.ac.uk/?author=2" title="View all posts by blogeditor" rel="author">blogeditor</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
